OL,3,CUK prisons are nearly at full
OL,4,Ccapacity, but what can be done?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Khadija Kothia
OL,8,FWith just over 1,400 spaces left for
OL,9,Fnew inmates, prisons across the UK are
OL,10,Fclose to breaking point, new figures
OL,11,Freveal.
OL,13,FThe total population stood at 87,453
OL,14,Fwith a "usable operational capacity"
OL,15,Fof 88,864 on Friday, just one day
OL,16,Fbefore newly elected Prime Minister
OL,17,FKeir Starmer highlighted
OL,18,Foverpopulation in prisons as part of
OL,19,Fhis government's key issues to tackle.
