OL,3,CUK prisons are nearly at full
OL,4,Ccapacity, but what can be done?
OL,6,FThis came under government plans to
OL,7,Ftackle overcrowding in Scottish
OL,8,Fprisons, which are in crisis and at
OL,9,Frisk of breaching inmates' human
OL,10,Frights, according to a new report
OL,11,Fpublished by Holyrood's Public Audit
OL,12,FCommittee.
OL,14,FThe issue is UK-wide. England and
OL,15,FWales have the highest per-person
OL,16,Fprison population in Western Europe.
OL,17,FScotland comes a close second.
