OL,3,CUK prisons are nearly at full
OL,4,Ccapacity, but what can be done?
OL,6,FThe highest number of people
OL,7,Fimprisoned was recorded less than a
OL,8,Fyear ago in October 2023, when the
OL,9,Fnumber reached 88,000.
OL,11,FUnder the previous administration, the
OL,12,FMinistry of Justice was already
OL,13,Fbuilding six new prisons to create an
OL,14,Fextra 20,000 places as demand grows
OL,15,Ffor cell spaces, with 6,000 spaces
OL,16,Falready being created.
OL,18,FLabour has previously said it wants to
OL,19,Fbuild more prisons, but whether this
OL,20,Fprogramme will continue under the new
OL,21,Fgovernment remains to be seen.
