OL,6,FThe backlog in the courts means there
OL,7,Fare many waiting at least months, if
OL,8,Fnot years, to be tried. Around two-
OL,9,Ffifths of this group are in the first
OL,10,Fcategory: not yet found guilty, and
OL,11,F40,424 people were sent to prison
OL,12,Fbefore their trial in 2022, an
OL,13,Fincrease of almost 13% compared with
OL,14,F2021.
