OL,7,Fproportion of remanded individuals due
OL,8,Fto their proximity to the courts are
OL,9,Fsome of the most overpopulated, says
OL,10,FDr Jenni Ward, Associate Professor of
OL,11,FCriminology at Middlesex University
OL,12,Fand convener of the Prisons Research
OL,13,FGroup (PRG).
