OL,6,FLike with many other social services,
OL,7,Fthe prisons budget has experienced
OL,8,Fsignificant cuts in recent years,
OL,9,Fdropping 20% between 2010/11 and 2014/
OL,10,F2015.
OL,12,FFrontline prison staff numbers were
OL,13,Falso cut by over a quarter between
OL,14,F2010-2017. Cuts in the budget and
OL,15,Fstaff numbers have impacted the
OL,16,Fprovision of adequate community
OL,17,Fsupervision, keeping prisoners inside
OL,18,Fwalls even till death, with elderly or
OL,19,Fdilapidated inmates taking up 10,700
OL,20,Fspaces.
